quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,50,"Na da ko Sogowan Ami in­onta na isa a lagid o sapuruk mata."
  54,51,"Na Sabunsabunar a bininasa Mi so manga lagid iyo sa kupit: Na ba adun a Phananadum?"
  54,52,"Na so langowan taman a pinggolaola iran noto na shisi-i ko manga daptar (a Pishoratan o man­ga Malaikat):"
  54,53,"Go omani maito, a go mala, na misosorat (ko Laokah makfod)."
  54,54,"Mata-an! A so Miyamanang­gila, na khatago ko manga Sorga, go manga lawasaig,"
  54,55,"Si-i ko darpa a bunar, o bai o (Allah a) Datu a Phakagaga."
  55,1,"So (Allah a) Masalinggagao!"
  55,2,"I Mindao ko Qur-an."
  55,3,"Inadun Niyan so Manosiya,"
  55,4,"Na Inindao Niyan non so la­lag."
  55,5,"So Alongan a go so Olan na si­-i ko itongan."
  55,6,"Na so mangunguto a pun­donapa, go so manga kayo na Mangangalimbaba-an siran (ko Masalinggagao)."
  55,7,"Na so Langit na ini poro lyan sukaniyan, go Inadun Niyan so timbangan,"
  55,8,"Ka angkano di khapokas ko ontol;"
  55,9,"Na pakambatanga niyo so kathimbang ko kaontol, go di kano phangorang ko timbangan."
  55,10,"Na so Lopa na kiyayat lyan sukaniyan sa baba a ruk o manga Ka-adun:"
  55,11,"Katatagowan sa manga Onga, go manga Qormah, a khibo-bongkosan,"
  55,12,"Go so manga Onga a maroni, a adun a manga ino-otiyan a go so mamot."
  55,13,"Na anda ko manga Limo o Kadnan niyo, i Pagongkirun niyo?"
  55,14,"Inadun Niyan so Manosiya a pho-on ko botha, a gango, a lagid o kiyomba,"
  55,15,"Go Inadun Niyan so Jinn a pho-on ko kadug o Apoi:"
  55,16,"Na anda ko manga Limo o Kadnan niyo, i Pagongkirun niyo?"